            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "\nMy experience for this school is not at all satisfactory.\nFirst of all for any activity theere are set of selected students who repeatedly gets chance to perform on stage .on asking to cordinator she responds back saying that we will give her chance in future but never gave my daughter a chance \nSecond teaching is just a simple ncert syallabus.nothing extra or out of box syllabus \nThird - in sports also selected students get chance to participate.they randomly select students to show the crowd and publicity and skating classes are not taken on regular basis even though my child has enrolled for same \nEvery year they increase money by 8 percentage as if we are working for them  for charity purpose.\nIn sr kg also they did not work in phonics sounds from the beginning and we had been informing them since long time still no improvement.\nAvoid this school if possible.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
