            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "How is IGCSE 11th grade in billabong international Hadapsar \nHow are the teachers and focus on academics and how’s it overall",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
