        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Billabong High International School - Hadapsar"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Sant Kumar Rai"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-03-14",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Outstanding Teachers and Exceptional Teaching!\n\nI am writing to express my sincere gratitude for the remarkable teaching and guidance to my son (Devansh Rai - Grade 1C) has received under your care.\n\nI would like to extend a special thanks to Ms. Neetu and  Ms. Lauren  Ma’am for their exceptional efforts in guiding and educating my son. Their passion for teaching and genuine care for my son's well-being have made a significant impact on his learning journey. Their dedication to fostering a supportive and inclusive classroom environment has contributed greatly to my son's overall development.\n\nAs a parent, it brings me immense joy and satisfaction to see my son thriving and enjoying his educational experience at Billabong High International School, Amanora (Hadapsar) Pune.\n\nThank you once again for creating such a nurturing and enriching learning environment for our children.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Billabong High International School - Hadapsar"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Poonam Prabhu Khorjuvenkar"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-02-21",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Few days back we landed from UK and I was looking out  for a good school for my daughter. I  visited Billabong school at Hadapsar. The infrastructure of the school is really good. After doing the school tour I really like this school a lot. As my husband office shifted to Hinjewadi we had to shift to Wakad. However I really liked this school and would definitely recommend this school to everyone.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Billabong High International School - Hadapsar"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "latha holla"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-02-09",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Sharing my honest review here. This is a good school. My son is studying in this school from 4 years in IGCSE (CAIE). Teachers, coordinator and principal are very cooperative and easily approachable. Teachers understand the child and provide necessary support. They do not discriminate, provide equal opportunity and my son is happy. So I am happy.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
