            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I'm not a parent but I came to billabong for a sports tournament and I suggest all you guys to never ever come here for tournament, the referee is extremely biased and in the favor of the school. I hope this message helps other sports players who do not want to waste their time in such tournaments.",
          "publisher": {
