        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Billabong High International School - Hadapsar"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Sandeep Sahdev"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-10-18",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Billabong High International School is one of the best schools among so many schools in Pune.\n\nI find the staff here are just so considerate, starting from the reception staff, I would like to name 2 individuals in the admin staff who are doing their job marvellously well, Sheetal and Smita... Kudos to you 🙏.\n\nAlso, I would like to mention the dynamic Principal, Mukherjee ma'am, who just impressed us on the first day itself that we visited this school.\n\nAll the teachers are just so warm and empathetic, especially my daughter's class teacher Ms. Prajakta and the grade 4 co-ordinator Ms. Adaline.\n\nThank you Billabong high school for providing the best conducive environment to my kid.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
