            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Kudos to the teachers and coordinator for organising a mini world tour for us…. I am sure each one of us vicariously traveled the world with amazing performances, set up and food…",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
