            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am happy & satisfied with the school. The environment was new for my kids but teachers made them feel comfortable.The Entire staff is very cooperative. I would like to mention that my son had a knee ligament injury the hole staff was very  helpful and taking care of him. Special thanks to all teachers for there support.",
